data.description: Located in the heart of Destin, surrounded by family-friendly activities, some of the world's most beautiful beaches, and great restaurants/bars, this turn-key condo has everything you're looking for in a second home or investment. The property features a heated pool, exercise room, restaurant, and onsite security. Unit comes fully furnished, including all appliances, indoor/outdoor furniture purchased new in 2021, T.V's purchased in 2021 Condo also has a new dishwasher, garbage disposal, and water heater is scheduled to be replaced. Relaxation is so close!
